<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>E</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa cu, Pathian a si, kha zeitik, hmanhah philh hlah
 A kan ser-tu cu, amah a si,
 Kan nih cu, a mi kan si, kan nih cu, a tuu kan si
 Bawipa cu, Kan Pa Pathian a si.

[C1]
   Thangthat u, thangthat u
   Bawipa cu, hla in thangthat u
   Thangthat u, thangthat u
   Bawipa cu, lawm in thangthat uh,
   Bawipa cu, Pathian a si, kha zeitik, hmanhah philh hlah
   Bawipa cu, Kan Pa Pathian a si.

[V2]
 Pathian cu, kan ca a ttha, a fek mi, a dawtnak cu
 Kan caah, a zung-zal in a hmun,
 Zumh awktlak, a sinak cu, chan vialte, tiangin a hmun
 Bawipa cu, Kan Pa Pathian a si.</lyrics>
<title>BAWIPA CU THANGTHAT A SI</title>
</song>